{"tid":2120712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生娘 vs 養娘","createTime":"2020-07-23T00:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T02:29:38.000Z","uid":268271,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41dfa58c87ba52d93e9a96f24ad86fa009d91c0d","tid":2120712,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T00:35:27.000Z","msg":"粵語殘片劇情, 背景音樂都係個隻。<br />\n假如, 你一出世就被生娘賣左, 養娘之後給你供書教學、教你知書識禮、明辨是非及放眼世界。<br />\n不旋踵, 你生娘變成暴發戶, 要求接你返去佢到住, 你及養娘無奈接受。<br />\n但是你不習慣生娘的生活型式, 生活得唔開心。<br />\n有日, 你在街上遇返養娘, 佢得知你生活得唔開心, 建議你跟返佢。<br />\n生娘得知你想跟返養娘, 佢話養娘干涉佢家事, 大發雷霆!<br />\n你正煩惱中, 在街上遇到港台麥嘉緯, 佢當然會問你 : 「想點？」<br />\n你會 :<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟返養娘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無奈接受生娘<br />\n<br />\n利申 :  以上故事純屬虛構，如有雷同實屬巧合<br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n1) 恭喜BNO持有者(藍屍除外)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2) 有無人知香港防空洞現價幾多錢尺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fbbb0af4a8d676b0b4146e7046d87abc262578","tid":2120712,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"從來唔係乜撚野生娘"},{"pid":"3982d71b7d4abd293229c0f55aa9777e70375323","tid":2120712,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T00:41:13.000Z","msg":"禁錯左負評<br />\n緊係跟養娘食生娘茶禮"},{"pid":"0e341199780480cbe850d6a4ad826160fd9b114e","tid":2120712,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4fbbb0af4a8d676b0b4146e7046d87abc262578","tid":2120712,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"從來唔係乜撚野生娘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T00:41:24.000Z","msg":"咪係..我未見過有人個仔